flowchart TB
    Pre["Before cycle<br/>staff_get"]
    Maint["Hour 1<br/>Human MAINT<br/>checklists / upkeep / small repairs"]
    Focus["Hours 2-4<br/>Human FOCUS<br/>one packet, one evidence target"]
    Post["After cycle<br/>staff_post<br/>evidence / next pointer / carry update"]
    Break["Mandatory break<br/>30-60 min after long focus"]

    subgraph StaffLane["Parallel staff lane"]
        Watch["staff_watch<br/>quiet sensing"]
        Get["staff_get<br/>compile checklist or focus packet"]
        Reingest["staff_post<br/>reingest touched state"]
    end

    Watch --> Get
    Get --> Pre
    Pre --> Maint
    Maint --> Focus
    Focus --> Post
    Post --> Reingest
    Reingest --> Break
    Break --> Watch